(Optional) Put a mini search box in the header
If you want a small search field on every page that links to /search/:

_includes/header.html (add inside the <nav> or beside the logo)


<form action="{{ '/search/' | relative_url }}" method="get" style="display:inline-block;margin-left:.75rem;">
  <input type="search" name="q" placeholder="Search…" onfocus="window.location=this.form.action" style="padding:.35rem .5rem;">
</form>


That simple version just sends people to the full search page. (If you prefer the live results dropdown in the header, we can wire that too—just say the word.)